Dear Mr. Lien,<br>
<br>
This week, I'll share how to qualify for special rates when booking a
cruise. Vacations To Go customers can sometimes receive exclusive
discounts from cruise lines based on specific qualifications, such as
age, occupation and past guest status.<br>
<br>
I have complied a list of specialty cruises, discounts and resources we
offer. Some are available only to certain types of travelers, and others
are available to all Vacations To Go customers. Click the links below
for more information:<br>
<br>
<a href="https://www.vacationstogo.com/senior_discounts.cfm?source=cruisemm&nr=cus_K6r_int&csp=K6rK6r&mmz=1">Age 55+ Rates</a><br>
<a href="https://www.vacationstogo.com/singles_cruises.cfm?source=cruisemm&nr=cus_K6r_int&csp=K6rK6r&mmz=1">Hosted Singles Cruises</a><br>
<a href="https://www.vacationstogo.com/interline_rates_search.cfm?source=cruisemm&nr=cus_K6r_int&csp=K6rK6r&mmz=1">Interline Rates</a><br>
<a href="https://www.vacationstogo.com/past_passenger.cfm?source=cruisemm&nr=cus_K6r_int&csp=K6rK6r&mmz=1">Past Passenger Rates</a><br>
<br>
Discount programs like these can be issued or withdrawn at any time by
the cruise line, and are not normally combinable with one another.
Always tell your Vacations To Go cruise counselor if you qualify for an
interline discount, are a past passenger of the line you are calling
about, or if anyone in the cabin will be 55+, so that he or she can make
sure to check for any additional discounts to which you may be
entitled.<br>
<br>
If you qualify for any of these special discounts and have not already
told us about it in My Account, you can
<a href="https://www.vacationstogo.com/emaillink.cfm?lnk=profile&email=liencf@gmail.com&nr=cus_K6r_pf&source=cruisemm&csp=K6rK6r&mmz=1">click here</a>
now to update your Special Discount Eligibility so we will always show
you the lowest rate you qualify for when you are browsing our website.<br>
<br><hr><br><!-- End of intro -->
